item.title: BONUS POSCAST: The Diamond King
item.description: It’s a bonus episode of the Poscast! Joe sits down with the guys from “The Diamond King” film: Director Marq Evans, Actor John Ortiz, and The Diamond King himself, Dick Perez. Feed: https://feeds.libsyn.com/565190/rss

item.title: Episode 452 w/ B.G.
item.description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode we chop it up with the one and only, B.G.!

The legendary New Orleans rapper and former Hot Boys member dives into his storied career, discussing his early days with Cash Money Records, the formation of the Hot Boys, and his influence on Southern hip-hop.

B.G. opens up about his time away from the spotlight, sharing personal insights and reflections... Feed: https://www.omnycontent.com/d/playlist/e73c998e-6e60-432f-8610-ae210140c5b1/9ff2dac3-12fd-4561-b512-ae33005f64f5/df6d181a-09ea-4bf2-adc6-ae33005f650d/podcast.rss
